@baseUrl = http://localhost:8096

###
### Spray API Tests
### Controller: SprayApiController
### Validation: @NotEmptyNotBlank on inputLinkList parameter (list must not be empty and contain no blank strings)
### Response: Returns plain text spray URL on success
### Error format: JSON {"error": "message"} for validation errors
###

### Spray links - Multiple valid URLs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=https://example.com&inputLinkList=https://google.com&
    inputLinkList=https://github.com
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - Two URLs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=https://example.com&inputLinkList=https://example.org
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - Single URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=https://example.com
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - URLs with different protocols
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=https://secure.example.com&inputLinkList=http://insecure.example.com
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - URLs with parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=https://example.com/search?q=test&inputLinkList=https://example.org/page?id=123
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - Empty list (expects 400 Bad Request - @NotEmptyNotBlank validation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - Invalid URLs (expects validation error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=not-a-url&inputLinkList=also-invalid
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - Mixed valid and invalid URLs (expects validation error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=https://example.com&inputLinkList=invalid-url
Accept: text/plain

### Spray links - Blank URLs (expects 400 Bad Request - @NotEmptyNotBlank validation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/spray?inputLinkList=&inputLinkList=https://example.com
Accept: text/plain

### Open spray links - Valid spray parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/spray/open?spray=https://example.com&spray=https://google.com
Accept: text/html